h4. Workaround
Disable and re-enable Service Desk

*Steps:*
# go to, _Manage add-ons_
# search for, Service Desk
# select, *Disable*
# select, *Enable*
(i) After completed, turn on email for the desired Service Desk

h3. NOTE: This issue is investigated to be slightly different from JSD-1407 as it is resolved previously. But the symptom and resolution method is the same.

This bug ticket is to track issues from {{16th March 2015}} onwards that running into the problem described below:

{quote}
